<h2>📈 Key Insights</h2>

<ul>
<li>Credit History is the most important factor</li>
<li>Higher income increases approval chances</li>
<li>Loan amount affects approval probability</li>
<li>Married applicants show higher approval rates</li>
<li>Urban applicants have better approval rates</li>
</ul>

